text: Harri Blumén (born 4 February 1958) is a Finnish ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1976 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Finland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1976 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Lahti
